item.title: Facebook For Developers - 29th September 2016, Dubai
item.description: Hi there, Here are couple of notes for the even I attended. We had a beautiful session starting from 9.50 am talking about how to monetize and distribute the facebook apps and some open source tools. Afterwards, there was a drill down into some technical topics explored in details in sort of a workshop. Interesting Technologies: Facebook Analytics for App - an free tool to track and analyze the behavior of the users within the facebook app.
